msg.msgText: A call to the setPriority() method on a message object or on a MessageProducer object failed because the input value is not a valid priority ({0}). Valid priority values are integers in the range 0 to 9.

msgExplanation.p: The setPriority() method was called on a Message object or on a MessageProducer object with a value that is not in the range of 0 to 9.

msgUserResponse.p: Use only valid priority values in the range 0 to 9.
